trait: kablui
version: 0.1

The KickAssBestLiveUserInterface trait adds a default user to the system,
named kablui, using SKEL_DIR=/etc/skel.kablui.

The kablui user will be configured and enabled as the gdmautologin user.

The kablui desktop philosophy can be summarized as
- vertical desktop toolbar on the left (with dmc's prefs)
- dark green background 0x125634
- ctrl up/down arrows cycle 6 virtual desktops
- ctrl right/left arrows cycle amonst terminal or browser tabs
- ctrl t create new terminal or browser tab

In the future, further enhancements will be made...
